---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Submission Guidelines" description="Rules and moderation policy for contributions.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p><strong>Submission Guidelines</strong></p>
    <h1>Write a useful story. Keep it factual and respectful.</h1>
    <p>These rules help us maintain practical and trustworthy career content.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="stack">
    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Required quality standard</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Describe day-to-day responsibilities with concrete examples.</li>
        <li>Include both positives and challenges.</li>
        <li>Give advice that students can act on.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>What we reject</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Defamatory, abusive, or unverifiable accusations.</li>
        <li>Promotion of scams or guaranteed-income claims.</li>
        <li>Personal data that should remain private.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Moderation process</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Submission enters the pending queue.</li>
        <li>Moderator reviews quality and safety criteria.</li>
        <li>Approved stories are published in the jobs directory.</li>
      </ol>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
